description: Incorrect Fact is a silly app that parodies Alexa's fact generating skill. Simply ask Alexa for a (incorrect) fact, and let her help you impress at your next cocktail party!
exampleInteractions: "Alexa, ask Incorrect Facts for a fact"
"Alexa, ask Incorrect Facts to give me an incorrect fact"
"Alexa, tell Incorrect Facts to give me some trivia"
name: Incorrect Facts
shortDescription: Alexa is full of (not so) useful information. Just ask her!
